data.description: Wonderfully maintained home in desirable Glen Laurel neighborhood! Enviting front porch, fenced yard with deck and patio for entertaining. Open split floor plan with BONUS room featuring vaulted ceiling in living area, formal dining room and wide foyer entrance. Master suite is completmented by a jacuzzi tub and large walk in closet with closet organizer shelving! Oversized gargage with shelving and cubbies too. Kitchen has granite counter tops, breakfast nook looking over the back yard, bar area and lots of cabinet space. Half bath is off of kitchen for convenience. Large laundry room - washer and dryer provided! Don't miss out on this immaculate home!
